{"tid":2336064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中左伏！！D**h Service Apartment","createTime":"2020-12-22T10:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T17:15:39.000Z","uid":360119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2f4d4f24fd2069dd408ed8aa326c0110237a68","tid":2336064,"uid":360119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"嘩 間野多伏到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簽左半年租約 入住第一日已經發現個冷氣係壞嘅 開到最凍 間房都係28-29度 仲高溫過出面 仲有一大隻小強 間房嘅衛生好差(多圖)<br />\n<br />\n住落仲多問題 個窗又漏水 啲燈又成日壞 間房仲成陣垃圾味 租之前話因爲疫情關係 唔比睇樓 當我中伏 呢啲我都算 但原來後面先黎料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKsOM4O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKsOM4O.png&h=7c9b4b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tEETKU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tEETKU.png&h=0799dd67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho2vfYk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho2vfYk.png&h=df282d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGmoAYp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGmoAYp.png&h=89f86d09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fbWVYu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fbWVYu.png&h=4a257ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PiwjTLe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPiwjTLe.png&h=74b579d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OV8Kkqj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOV8Kkqj.png&h=fed95d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cygv0qp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCygv0qp.png&h=41bcc189&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHdeHDR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHdeHDR.png&h=7cbd41b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcvQfYY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcvQfYY.png&h=cc8f0cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n住左唔夠一星期個guest service就話要黎檢查廚房排水管 話一年檢查一次 一個月後出面搭哂棚 問個guest service又話佢地乜都唔知 我自己走去問管理處先知個大廈成年前已經傾要更換外牆水管 不過就話唔洗入單位搞 咁搞法成日唔開得窗 又要落窗簾 心諗又中伏了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過左一個月 guest service都冇答我到底出面要裝修啲乜 (佢地聲稱自己唔係業主 亦從來唔知大廈出面要做維修) 只係話要黎睇個單位 但又唔講要做乜 打電話問先知佢地話要睇出面啲水管整得好唔好 又話如果唔比佢地上黎檢查 到時發現有咩問題個租客要負責 咁都得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又過左一個月 guest service又話要黎睇廚房個排水管 話要睇粒幾鐘 問佢要睇啲咩睇咁耐 佢先話係要黎換廚房個排水管！同佢地講話咁對我影響太大 唔想佢地係我租期內做維修 佢地就話可以&rdquo;幫我&rdquo;延期到下個月 話做維修係為左令個居住環境更好 作為service apartment 佢地嘅service真係不得了<br />\n<br />\n個個月走黎煩我 又咩都唔講清楚 租之前唔講 租左之後問佢地就咩都話唔知 但就成日走黎煩住哂 呢間公司真係冇得頂<br />\n<br />\n簽約之前講到佢自己啲cleansing service有幾咁high standard 但現實係啲毛巾呀 被呀 床單呀 勁多頭髮 啲櫃又發霉 唔知下個中伏嘅係邊個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd02d647d4c99ff6678b6355788b922a0a1851d3","tid":2336064,"uid":149522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"佢都係話疫情唔比睇，好彩無租⋯⋯"}]}